### Create a new message
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "email do mais brabo",
  "userId": "26c631c3-57b5-41c7-beb9-bc44de1f53f7",
  "email": "claro@imusica.com.br",
  "scheduledTime": "2025-11-13T10:00:00Z"
}

### Create a message scheduled for now (immediate processing)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "Urgent message - process immediately!",
  "email": "urgent@example.com",
  "scheduledTime": "2025-11-13T00:00:00Z"
}

### Create a message scheduled for future
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "This message is scheduled for tomorrow.",
  "email": "future@example.com",
  "scheduledTime": "2025-11-14T15:30:00Z"
}

### Get message by ID (replace with actual ID from create response)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/messages/42a85a92-1942-4095-a964-afae4b58760c

### Get all messages (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/messages

### Get all messages (custom pagination - page 0, size 5)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/messages?page=0&size=10

### Get all messages (page 1, size 10)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/messages?page=1&size=10

### Get all messages (sorted by scheduledTime descending)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/messages?sort=scheduledTime,desc

